QUr'a-N'a HYSh 'yVNK V'aL-MY MQDShYM ThPhNH.
KY-L'aVYL YHUrG-K'ySh VPhThH ThMYTh QN'aH.
'aNY-Ur'aYThY 'aVYL MShUrYSh V'aQVB NVHV PhTh'aM.
YUrChQV BNYV MYSh'y VYDK'aV BSh'yUr V'aYN MTShYL.
'aShUr QTShYUrV Ur'yB Y'aKL V'aL-MTShNYM YQChHV VSh'aPh TShMYM ChYLM.
KY L'a-YTSh'a M'yPhUr 'aVN VM'aDMH L'a-YTShMCh 'yML.
KY-'aDM L'yML YVLD VBNY-UrShPh YGBYHV 'yVPh.
'aVLM 'aNY 'aDUrSh 'aL-'aL V'aL-'aLHYM 'aShYM DBUrThY.
'yShH GDLVTh V'aYN ChQUr NPhL'aVTh 'yD-'aYN MSPhUr.
HNThN MTUr 'yL-PhNY-'aUrTSh VShLCh MYM 'yL-PhNY ChVTShVTh.
LShVM ShPhLYM LMUrVM VQDUrYM ShGBV YSh'y.
MPhUr MChShBVTh 'yUrVMYM VL'a-Th'yShYNH YDYHM ThVShYH.
LKD ChKMYM B'yUrMM V'yTShTh NPhThLYM NMHUrH.
YVMM YPhGShV-ChShK VKLYLH YMShShV BTShHUrYM.
VYSh'y MChUrB MPhYHM VMYD ChZQ 'aBYVN.
VThHY LDL ThQVH V'yLThH QPhTShH PhYH.
HNH 'aShUrY 'aNVSh YVKChNV 'aLVH VMVSUr ShDY 'aL-ThM'aS.
KY HV'a YK'aYB VYChBSh YMChTSh VYDV ThUrPhYNH.
